    "This was easy because all the silicon participants included a response like the following early in their interview: \"Researcher: Good morning Robert, thank you for agreeing to participate in our study on physical activity in older adults.",
    "Can you tell me a bit about your current physical activity level?",
    "Here is a more typical, less extreme, example: \"Researcher: What are you able to do physically?",
    "James: Physically, I am able to do some light activities such as walking and light gardening, but I have to be careful not to overexert myself.",
    "I have to avoid high-intensity activities and heavy lifting."
  ],
